name: Anagram 12. (New Years 2021 Edition)
description:
Augmented Reality Digital Sculpture: Glitched "Cyborg" Face with Iridescent and Neon-Purple Textures Staring into Space.

"Anagram 12." is a a special New Years digital sculpture for my collectors who have generously supported my art in 2021. Thank you all! The impact you have made in my life is invaluable. I've learned so much about myself in the 2.5 months that I've been apart of the NFT community and I can't wait to continue this journey into 2022. Much love.

-Micah
